<p class="short-reference" data-aid="154411049" id="short_reference1">&#x201C;August 19&#x2013;25. Alma 53&#x2013;63,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
<header>
<figure class="image no-print" id="figure1">
